survey_response.review_text: We are so fortunate to get doctor like Suvarna madam as first of all doctor could connect to us well in our concern, listened to our issue completely as we were so worried that my son had 104 degree temperature for almost 2days as we were thinking it could be a sign of dengue but doctor asked most important questions to us like how is his intake, how is activities, whether he is active or not, etc we answered to all the questions then Doctor Suvarna madam suggested us to wait for one more day as he is completely alright no need to worry. Doctor Suvarna madam could gave us complete clarity and confidence to us that it's not dengue pls rest be assured no need to go for any tests. We were so impressed with madam advice as it was so helpful for us to take further action being parents and also suggested us not to go for any antibiotics that really talks about doctor involvement with the patient.We highly impressed with Doctor Suvarna madam and we suggested to our neighbours, relatives & friends about madam. We thank once again Doctor Suvarna madam for guiding us in right direction as madam diagnosed our son correctly.Thank you madam once again.
